            as the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Norwalk</ENAMEX> virus and related viruses (Figures <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">1</NUMEX>,
            <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">4</NUMEX>). These <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">proteins</ENAMEX> could potentially function as a
