            cellular <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">homologs</ENAMEX>. All the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">members</ENAMEX> of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">LRAT</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">family</ENAMEX>,
